<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.3">
<l>muṉṉōr tūtu vāṉarattiṉ vāyil moḻintarakkaṉ</l>
<l>maṉṉūr taṉṉai vāḷiyiṉāl māḷa muṉintavaṉē</l>
<l>piṉṉōr tūta ṉātimaṉṉark kākip perunilattā</l>
<l>riṉṉār tūta ṉeṉaniṉṟā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having once expressed a message through the mouth of a monkey,</l>
<l>The same one who raged at the demon’s strong city to destroy it</l>
<l rend="indent">with an arrow,</l>
<l>He who later, becoming a messenger for the high king, stood [firm]</l>
<l>As those of the great world said, “He is [just] a messenger of the enemy,”</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
